      "writtenOn": "2020-07-31T03:20:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Strictly speaking reading cls.Handler will be a race if someone calls AttachHandler at the same time. Reading it under the lock is strictly speaking more correct. In practice no one will likely call AttachHandler concurrently, but reading under the lock is not hard, so I implemented it.",
